  "fullArabic": "وَٱلَّذِينَ يُتَوَفَّوۡنَ مِنكُمۡ وَيَذَرُونَ أَزۡوَٰجٗا يَتَرَبَّصۡنَ بِأَنفُسِهِنَّ أَرۡبَعَةَ أَشۡهُرٖ وَعَشۡرٗاۖ فَإِذَا بَلَغۡنَ أَجَلَهُنَّ فَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَيۡكُمۡ فِيمَا فَعَلۡنَ فِيٓ أَنفُسِهِنَّ بِٱلۡمَعۡرُوفِۗ وَٱللَّهُ بِمَا تَعۡمَلُونَ خَبِيرٞ",
  "fullTranslation": "And those who are taken in death among you and leave wives behind - they, [the wives, shall] wait four months and ten [days]. And when they have fulfilled their term, then there is no blame upon you for what they do with themselves in an acceptable manner. And Allah is [fully] Acquainted with what you do.",
  "fullTransliteration": "wa-alladhina yutawaffawna minkum wayadharuna azwajan yatarabbasna bi-anfusihinna arba'ata ashhurin wa'ashran fa-idha balaghna ajalahunna fala junaha alaykum fima fa'alna fi anfusihinna bil-ma'rufi wal-lahu bima ta'maluna khabirun"
